                </div>
                <p class="text-green-300 text-xs p-3 leading-relaxed">
                  1944. Submarino sin ox√≠geno. Encuentra los 6 tanques escondidos.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4 bg-black border-2 border-green-500 p-3 relative">
              <div class="absolute -top-1 -left-1 w-2 h-2 bg-green-500"></div>
              <div class="absolute -top-1 -right-1 w-2 h-2 bg-green-500"></div>
              <div class="absolute -bottom-1 -left-1 w-2 h-2 bg-green-500"></div>
              <div class="absolute -bottom-1 -right-1 w-2 h-2 bg-green-500"></div>
              <p class="text-xs text-green-300 pixel-text text-center">
